Module io.helidon.webclient
Package io.helidon.webclient

Interface WebClientRequestHeaders

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Headers, Parameters
    public interface WebClientRequestHeaders
extends Headers
    Headers that can be modified (until request is sent) for outbound request.
